#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Create activities in the CRM to ensure you're keeping track of open "
"opportunities"
msgstr ""
"ສ້າງກິດຈະກຳໃນ CRM ເພື່ອຮັບປະກັນວ່າທ່ານກຳລັງຕິດຕາມໂອກາດການຂາຍທີ່ຍັງເປີດຢູ່"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model:pos.payment.method,name:food_trucks.pos_payment_method_3
msgid "Customer Account"
msgstr "ບັນຊີລູກຄ້າ"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Did you know you can also get a full <strong>Accounting</strong> suite in "
"Odoo?"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຮູ້ບໍ່ວ່າ ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດນຳໃຊ້ລະບົບ <strong>ການບັນຊີ</strong> ແບບຄົບວົງຈອນໃນ Odoo ໄດ້?"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Do You Want to Go Further?"
msgstr "ທ່ານຕ້ອງການໄປໄກກວ່ານີ້ບໍ?"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model:hr.department,name:food_trucks.hr_department_2
msgid "Employees"
msgstr "ພະນັກງານ"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model:crm.tag,name:food_trucks.crm_tag_2
msgid "Event"
msgstr "ງານກິດຈະກຳ"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Explore extra Odoo apps that might be interesting for your specific "
"business, they're all included in your subscription !"
msgstr ""
"ສຶກສາແອັບເພີ່ມເຕີມຂອງ Odoo ທີ່ອາດຈະໜ້າສົນໃຈສຳລັບທຸລະກິດສະເພາະຂອງທ່ານ, ເຊິ່ງທັງໝົດລວມຢູ່ໃນຄ່າບໍລິການ"
"ຂອງທ່ານແລ້ວ!"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Field Service Documentation"
msgstr "ເອກະສານຄູ່ມືການບໍລິການນອກສະຖານທີ່"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model:crm.tag,name:food_trucks.crm_tag_6
msgid "Full Day"
msgstr "ເຕັມມື້"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model:product.template,name:food_trucks.product_product_32_product_template
msgid "Full day"
msgstr "ເຕັມມື້"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model:crm.tag,name:food_trucks.crm_tag_3
#: model:product.template,name:food_trucks.product_product_31_product_template
msgid "Half Day"
msgstr "ເຄິ່ງມື້"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model:uom.uom,name:food_trucks.uom_uom_29
msgid "Half Days"
msgstr "ເຄິ່ງມື້"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Handle all your customers in a breeze and get a nice overview of your income"
" through the reporting features that are integrated in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"ຈັດການລູກຄ້າທັງໝົດຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍ ແລະ ເບິ່ງພາບລວມຂອງລາຍໄດ້ຜ່ານຄຸນສົມບັດການອອກລາຍງານທີ່ມີຢູ່ໃ"
"ນ Odoo."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If applicable, you can invoice your presence to your customer through the "
"invoice app. You can configure your invoice templates to include terms &amp;"
" conditions, as well as other handy features."
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າເປັນໄປໄດ້, ທ່ານສາມາດອອກໃບແຈ້ງໜີ້ໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າຜ່ານແອັບໃບແຈ້ງໜີ້. ທ່ານສາມາດຕັ້ງຄ່າຮູບແບບໃບແຈ້ງໜີ້ເພື່ອລວມ"
"ເອົາເງື່ອນໄຂຕ່າງໆ ແລະ ຄຸນສົມບັດທີ່ສະດວກອື່ນໆ."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If applicable, you can of course directly manage your events directly in the"
" Field service app without going through the CRM and Sales app."
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າເປັນໄປໄດ້, ທ່ານສາມາດຈັດການງານກິດຈະກຳຂອງທ່ານໃນແອັບການບໍລິການນອກສະຖານທີ່ໄດ້ໂດຍກົງ ໂດຍບໍ່ຕ້ອງຜ່"
"ານແອັບ CRM ແລະ ການຂາຍ."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you want to easily discover every features of this package, try "
"downloading the Demo Data."
msgstr ""
"ຫາກທ່ານຕ້ອງການສຶກສາທຸກຄຸນສົມບັດຂອງແພັກເກດນີ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍ, ລອງດາວໂຫຼດຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງ (Demo Data)."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"In some cases, you will get bookings from customers (coporate, etc.) for you"
" to attend an company event or other similar events."
msgstr ""
"ໃນບາງກໍລະນີ, ທ່ານຈະໄດ້ຮັບການຈອງຈາກລູກຄ້າ (ບໍລິສັດ, ແລະ ອື່ນໆ) ເພື່ອໃຫ້ທ່ານໄປຮ່ວມງານກິດຈະກຳຂອງບໍລິ"
"ສັດ ຫຼື ງານອື່ນໆ ທີ່ຄ້າຍຄືກັນ."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Incoming opportunities can be registered into your CRM. Manage opportunity "
"stages in the kanban view, categorization using tags, to-do's and reminders "
"using activities, and communication through the chatter."
msgstr ""
"ໂອກາດການຂາຍທີ່ເຂົ້າມາສາມາດລົງທະບຽນໃນ CRM ຂອງທ່ານ. ຈັດການຂັ້ນຕອນໂອກາດໃນມຸມມອງຄານບານ "
"(kanban), ຈັດໝວດໝູ່ໂດຍໃຊ້ແທັກ, ລາຍການທີ່ຕ້ອງເຮັດ ແລະ ການແຈ້ງເຕືອນໂດຍໃຊ້ກິດຈະກຳ, ແລະ ການຕິດຕໍ່"
"ສື່ສານຜ່ານຊ່ອງສົນທະນາ."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Install the <strong>Social Marketing App </strong>to manage your social "
"media presence."
msgstr ""
"ຕິດຕັ້ງ <strong>ແອັບການຕະຫຼາດຜ່ານສື່ສັງຄົມອອນລາຍ</strong> ເພື່ອຈັດການການມີຕົວຕົນໃນສື່ສັງຄົມຂອງທ່າ"
"ນ."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Invoice your customers using the <strong>Invoice app</strong>"
msgstr "ອອກໃບແຈ້ງໜີ້ໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າຂອງທ່ານໂດຍໃຊ້ <strong>ແອັບໃບແຈ້ງໜີ້</strong>"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Invoicing Documentation"
msgstr "ເອກະສານຄູ່ມືການອອກໃບແຈ້ງໜີ້"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Just be careful, once demo data are uploaded, it cannot be easily deleted. "
"But you can restart a fresh database on"
msgstr ""
"ຂໍໃຫ້ລະມັດລະວັງ, ເມື່ອອັບໂຫຼດຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງແລ້ວ ຈະບໍ່ສາມາດລຶບອອກໄດ້ງ່າຍໆ. ແຕ່ທ່ານສາມາດເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຖານຂໍ້ມູນໃໝ່"
"ໄດ້ທີ່"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Manage your <strong>Purchases and Inventory</strong> in Odoo as well."
msgstr ""
"ຈັດການ <strong>ການຈັດຊື້ ແລະ ສິນຄ້າຄົງຄັງ</strong> ຂອງທ່ານໃນ Odoo ໄດ້ເຊັ່ນກັນ."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage your presence at events using the <strong>Field Service app</strong>"
msgstr ""
"ຈັດການການໄປຮ່ວມງານກິດຈະກຳຕ່າງໆ ໂດຍໃຊ້ <strong>ແອັບການບໍລິການນອກສະຖານທີ່</strong>"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model:crm.tag,name:food_trucks.crm_tag_7
msgid "Multi-Day"
msgstr "ຫຼາຍມື້"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Need a Website? No problem, Odoo can do it as well."
msgstr "ຕ້ອງການເວັບໄຊບໍ? ບໍ່ມີບັນຫາ, Odoo ສາມາດເຮັດໃຫ້ໄດ້ເຊັ່ນກັນ."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Odoo.com/trial"
msgstr "Odoo.com/trial"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once you have all the information regarding this opportunity, you can make a"
" new quotation. Define how long you'll be staying, and if relevant, other "
"things you will be charging to the customer."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອທ່ານມີຂໍ້ມູນທັງໝົດກ່ຽວກັບໂອກາດນີ້ແລ້ວ, ທ່ານສາມາດສ້າງໃບສະເໜີລາຄາໃໝ່. ກຳນົດໄລຍະເວລາທີ່ທ່ານຈະໄປໃຫ້"
"ບໍລິການ ແລະ ສິ່ງອື່ນໆ ທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງທີ່ທ່ານຈະເກັບເງິນນຳລູກຄ້າ."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Point of Sale Documentation"
msgstr "ເອກະສານຄູ່ມືລະບົບໜ້າຮ້ານ (POS)"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Reach us"
msgstr "ຕິດຕໍ່ພວກເຮົາ"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Sales Documentation"
msgstr "ເອກະສານຄູ່ມືການຂາຍ"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Send quotations to prospective customers through the <strong>Sales "
"app</strong>"
msgstr "ສົ່ງໃບສະເໜີລາຄາໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າທີ່ຄາດຫວັງຜ່ານ <strong>ແອັບການຂາຍ</strong>"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Take a look at the <strong>Email Marketing App</strong> to let past "
"customers know what you're up to !"
msgstr ""
"ລອງໃຊ້ <strong>ແອັບການຕະຫຼາດຜ່ານອີເມວ</strong> ເພື່ອແຈ້ງໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າເກົ່າຮູ້ກ່ຽວກັບການເຄື່ອນໄຫວຂອງທ່"
"ານ!"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Use the <strong>CRM app</strong> to manage your opportunities"
msgstr "ໃຊ້ <strong>ແອັບ CRM</strong> ເພື່ອຈັດການໂອກາດການຂາຍຂອງທ່ານ"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:web_tour.tour,rainbow_man_message:food_trucks.knowledge_tour
msgid "Welcome! Happy exploring."
msgstr "ຍິນດີຕ້ອນຮັບ! ຂໍໃຫ້ມ່ວນກັບການສຶກສາລະບົບ."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When your prospective customer confirms the sale, a new task is created in your field service app, and linked back to your sale order. You can manage assignations, needs, and so on from there and obtain a handy overview of your\n"
"        planning."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອລູກຄ້າທີ່ຄາດຫວັງຢືນຢັນການສັ່ງຊື້, ໜ້າວຽກໃໝ່ຈະຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນໃນແອັບການບໍລິການນອກສະຖານທີ່ຂອງທ່ານ ແລະ ເຊື່"
"ອມໂຍງກັບໃບສັ່ງຂາຍ. ທ່ານສາມາດຈັດການການມອບໝາຍວຽກ, ຄວາມຕ້ອງການ ແລະ ອື່ນໆ ຈາກບ່ອນນັ້ນ ແລະ ເບິ່"
"ງພາບລວມຂອງ\n"
"        ການວາງແຜນຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ຢ່າງສະດວກ."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"While on the field, you can take orders and payments from your customers or from the attendees through the Point of Sale app. The app is a fully featured point-of-sale solution that supports menus, products, quantities, discounts,\n"
"        pricelists, custom notes, and many other features."
msgstr ""
"ໃນຂະນະທີ່ຢູ່ໜ້າວຽກ, ທ່ານສາມາດຮັບການສັ່ງຊື້ ແລະ ຊຳລະເງິນຈາກລູກຄ້າ ຫຼື ຜູ້ເຂົ້າຮ່ວມງານຜ່ານແອັບ Point "
"of Sale. ແອັບນີ້ແມ່ນລະບົບໜ້າຮ້ານທີ່ຄົບວົງຈອນ ເຊິ່ງຮອງຮັບທັງ ເມນູ, ສິນຄ້າ, ຈຳນວນ, ສ່ວນຫຼຸດ,\n"
"        ລາຍການລາຄາ, ບັນທຶກເພີ່ມເຕີມ ແລະ ຄຸນສົມບັດອື່ນໆ ອີກຫຼາກຫຼາຍ."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"With the Food Trucks Industry Package, you have all you need to manage your "
"business from customer bookings to invoicing, including a point-of-sale "
"system and much more."
msgstr ""
"ດ້ວຍແພັກເກດທຸລະກິດລົດຂາຍອາຫານ, ທ່ານມີທຸກຢ່າງທີ່ຈຳເປັນໃນການຈັດການທຸລະກິດ ຕັ້ງແຕ່ການຈອງຂອງລູກຄ້າໄປຈົ"
"ນເຖິງການອອກໃບແຈ້ງໜີ້, ລວມທັງລະບົບໜ້າຮ້ານ ແລະ ອື່ນໆ ອີກຫຼາຍຢ່າງ."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Would you like to discuss your Odoo setup with us or explore more features?"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຕ້ອງການປຶກສາກ່ຽວກັບການຕິດຕັ້ງ Odoo ຂອງທ່ານກັບພວກເຮົາ ຫຼື ສຶກສາຄຸນສົມບັດເພີ່ມເຕີມບໍ?"

